  satisfactory performance of the member of staff over the period of
  the convertible contract. For members of staff assigned to a post
  below the I band, the conversion decision is taken by the Director
  General Human Resources or their Deputy, after consulting the
  Director General or Director of the business area in which the
  member of staff is employed, at least six months prior to the expiry
  of the convertible contract. (ECB Staff Rules, pages 44–45)
